casebody.data:
Van Etten, Respondent, v. Newton et al., Appellants. (Common Pleas of New York, City and County, General Term. April 7, 1890.)

Argued before Larrbmore, C. J., and Daly and Bisohoff, JJ.

E. D. McCarthy, for appellants. Hyland & Zabriske, for respondent.

No opinion. Motion for leave to appeal.to the court of appeals granted. See 6 N. Y. Supp. 531; 7 N. Y. Supp. 663; 8 N. Y. Supp. 478.
